  "body": "<p>One of the prompts at Two Peas this month is a focus on patterned papers. I decided to use my favorite combinations of patterns - woodgrain, polka dots and florals to create a colorful layout. I used some behind the scenes photos from the <a href=\"http://www.tbs.com/shows/trendswithbenefits/video/video-detail/hipster-scrapbooking\">TBS Trends With Benefits</a> shoot at Urbanic. Here is how this page came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"11a-DSC_1723-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/47369645f29ca449.jpg?v=1782525736\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"11b-DSC_1724-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a0f3762ce5f58ad9.jpg?v=1782525739\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11c-DSC_1725-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7267feee3d62b304.jpg?v=1782525742\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11d-DSC_1726-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/21cc08dfc36d19b3.jpg?v=1782525745\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11ee-DSC_1728-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0ce1fc2e35dbba46.jpg?v=1782525747\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11f-DSC_1731-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d13352411f2853d0.jpg?v=1782525750\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11g-DSC_1732-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/831619e5897e9eeb.jpg?v=1782525753\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11h-DSC_1733-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d3cf1d03c81fbe9a.jpg?v=1782525756\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11i-DSC_1734-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/308b208b95a950ea.jpg?v=1782525759\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11j-DSC_1735-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/592229ebc8031994.jpg?v=1782525762\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11k-DSC_1738-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/595ce248e7a5634a.jpg?v=1782525764\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11l-DSC_1747-598x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/019a12d339d6b30f.jpg?v=1782525767\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>If you're wondering, I did use the make up artist's hair as inspiration for the layout. Copyright Two Peas In A Bucket</p>"
